[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Magic bulldozer]]
'''Magic Bulldozer''' is a [[en/Manual/Cheats|cheat]] that enables the user to destroy anything including industries, lighthouses, etc. This can be useful if a town will not let you destroy a house for example when you want to build a railway through that tile.

